items.headline: Welcome to the Sonic for Hire Wikia!
items.desc: Sonic For Hire Wiki is the online encyclopaedia dedicated to everything Sonic For Hire, a series following Sonic the Hedgehog as he is washed up and kicked out of work. This wiki covers the many seasons, episodes and characters from Sonic For Hire. For up-to-date information about everything Sonic For Hire, check out this shreddy wiki!
